        </div>
        <div class="multi-links" style="margin-top:12px;">
          <a class="multi-link" href="https://www.nzstuntschool.com/event/urban-combat-skills-drills-monthly-training-july-2026/4025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="background:rgba(74,124,89,0.2);border-color:rgba(74,124,89,0.5);color:#6ab882;">📅 Book Session 1 →</a>
          <a class="multi-link" href="https://www.nzstuntschool.com/event/urban-combat-camera-performance-monthly-training-aug-2026/4026/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="background:rgba(74,124,89,0.1);border-color:rgba(74,124,89,0.3);color:#6ab882;">+ Session 2 →</a>
          <a class="multi-link" href="https://www.nzstuntschool.com/event/urban-combat-scenario-day-monthly-training-sep-2026/6737/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="background:rgba(74,124,89,0.1);border-color:rgba(74,124,89,0.3);color:#6ab882;">+ Session 3 →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="event-note" style="margin-top:8px;color:#6ab882;">💰 Book all 3 for $160 and save $20</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

